      <title>英国石油公司拒绝增加英国工人养老金支付的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bp-rejects-uk-retirees-request-for-extra-pension-payout-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司(BP Plc)今年拒绝将向英国退休工人支付的固定福利金额外提高2%，称其养老金支付速度在过去十年中已经超过了通胀率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/bp-rejects-uk-retirees-request-for-extra-pension-payout-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
